.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: light-blue, amber, ivory, grey, chestnut
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, polish, turkish, indian, canadian
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, hot-chocolate, iced-tea, mirinda
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: light-vegafina, cain, siglo, oliveros, swisher
5 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, rabbit, ferret, hedgehog, snake
1. the argentine is the person who likes ivory
2. the swedish is the owner of the ferret
3. the polish is the person drinking iced-tea
4. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes grey
5. the person who likes amber is the person drinking sprite
6. the siglo-smoker is the owner of the rabbit
7. the person who likes chestnut is the cain-smoker
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in the middle
9. the indian is on the far left
10. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig
11. the owner of the snakes is on the left or right of the cain-smoker
12. the light-vegafina-smoker is the person drinking cola
13. the turkish is the oliveros-smoker
14. the indian is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue
15. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    chestnut	|     light-blue	|      ivory	|     amber	|     grey	|
| Nationality	|   indian	|    polish	|    argentine	|    turkish	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     guinea-pig	|    snake	|     rabbit	|     hedgehog	|      ferret	|
| Beverage	|    mirinda	|     iced-tea	|     hot-chocolate	|    sprite	|      cola	|
| Cigar		|   cain	|    swisher	|  siglo	|    oliveros	|   light-vegafina	|
